---
---

<section class="technicians" id="technicians">
  <div class="technicians__bg">
    <!-- Floating icons -->
    <div class="technicians__icon technicians__icon--1">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
        <circle cx="30" cy="16" r="10"></circle>
        <path d="M16 44c0-10 6-16 14-16s14 6 14 16"></path>
        <path d="M44 30c4-2 6 0 4 4"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="technicians__icon technicians__icon--2">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
        <rect x="10" y="20" width="40" height="28" rx="2"></rect>
        <rect x="20" y="8" width="20" height="12" rx="1"></rect>
        <line x1="10" y1="48" x2="6" y2="54"></line>
        <line x1="50" y1="48" x2="54" y2="54"></line>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="technicians__icon technicians__icon--3">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path d="M20 50 C20 30 20 20 30 10 C40 20 40 30 40 50"></path>
        <line x1="30" y1="10" x2="30" y2="50"></line>
        <path d="M15 50 C15 35 15 25 25 15"></path>
        <path d="M45 50 C45 35 45 25 35 15"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="technicians__icon technicians__icon--4">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
        <circle cx="20" cy="24" r="12"></circle>
        <circle cx="40" cy="24" r="12"></circle>
        <circle cx="20" cy="40" r="12"></circle>
        <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="12"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="technicians__icon technicians__icon--5">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
        <rect x="8" y="28" width="44" height="24" rx="2"></rect>
        <path d="M16 28V16c0-2 2-4 4-4h20c2 0 4 2 4 4v12"></path>
        <circle cx="20" cy="40" r="3"></circle>
        <circle cx="30" cy="40" r="3"></circle>
        <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="3"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="technicians__icon technicians__icon--6">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path d="M30 8L8 22v28h44V22L30 8z"></path>
        <rect x="22" y="32" width="16" height="18"></rect>
        <line x1="8" y1="22" x2="52" y2="22"></line>
        <circle cx="30" cy="16" r="3"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="technicians__content container">
    <h2 class="technicians__title">
      ¡Potenciando el monitoreo inteligente para Técnicos Agrícolas!
    </h2>
    <p class="technicians__text">
      Nuestra plataforma pone en manos de técnicos y asesores agrícolas la
      tecnología más avanzada en sensores IA para la detección de plagas.
      Olvídate de los desplazamientos innecesarios para revisar trampas
      manuales; nuestra red de sensores monitorea cada rincón del olivar por ti,
      enviando conteos precisos de mosca del olivo y alertas en tiempo real
      directamente a tu oficina o móvil.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .technicians {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-turquoise);
    padding: 100px 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .technicians__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .technicians__icon {
    position: absolute;
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .technicians__icon--1 {
    top: 10%;
    left: 5%;
  }
  .technicians__icon--2 {
    top: 8%;
    right: 8%;
  }
  .technicians__icon--3 {
    bottom: 10%;
    left: 8%;
  }
  .technicians__icon--4 {
    top: 50%;
    left: 15%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }
  .technicians__icon--5 {
    bottom: 12%;
    right: 5%;
  }
  .technicians__icon--6 {
    top: 50%;
    right: 12%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .technicians__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .technicians__title {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-white);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .technicians__text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .technicians {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .technicians__title {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
    .technicians__icon {
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
    }
  }
</style>
